{"tid":919751,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[屯門牛屎地方，極低層唔計]【第二波劈價】屯門620呎三房私樓 500萬成交","createTime":"2018-11-28T09:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T03:18:52.000Z","uid":70301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cef42d638825d8a0224f8f226c2ccc09be43f6a3","tid":919751,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T09:37:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181128/58968156\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181128%2F58968156&d=%2BWpD9ZlUq4iJirSvHYEh%2BP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ee91d632\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181128%2F58968156&h=cbb21f83\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181128/58968156</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181128/large/1543387020_e74b.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181128%2Flarge%2F1543387020_e74b.jpg&d=%2BWpD9ZlUq4iJirSvHYEh%2BP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=36095cd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181128/large/1543387020_e74b.jpg</a><br />\n恆豐園三房造價低見500萬元，平絕屯門私樓。<br />\n<br />\n樓市出現第二波劈價，屯門三房私樓快見「四字頭」，抵買過居屋。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，恆豐園3座極低層G室，實用面積620方呎，屬屋苑最大單位，三房連主人套房間隔，原叫價600萬元，放盤約三個月，剛減價「1球」至500萬元成交，呎價8,065元，料平絕屯門私樓三房，重返去年10月水平。同座同層A室，屬細三房，593方呎，今年2月成交價也要503萬元，呎價8,482元。屋苑同面積單位，今年6月高位造價663萬元，是次成交較高位回落25%。代理直言，「平到冇朋友」，但裝修超殘，業主自住。"},{"pid":"09fb15930a42042f64ae41f8f6c31531bd61922d","tid":919751,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T17:11:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c52e3d0365de480f4ec718cdc83deee8608ce99","tid":919751,"uid":30109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime